    <mxCell id="2" value="Interpretable Prediction &amp; Explanation  (shared across both domains)" style="text;html=1;strokeColor=none;fillColor=none;align=center;verticalAlign=middle;whiteSpace=wrap;rounded=0;fontSize=15;fontStyle=1;" vertex="1" parent="1"><mxGeometry x="10" y="10" width="1160" height="38" as="geometry" /></mxCell>
    <mxCell id="3" value="Intentionally linear classifier — interpretability requires linearity  ·  Accuracy vs explainability trade-off is explicitly tested in ablations" style="text;html=1;strokeColor=none;fillColor=none;align=center;verticalAlign=middle;whiteSpace=wrap;rounded=0;fontSize=11;fontStyle=2;" vertex="1" parent="1"><mxGeometry x="10" y="50" width="1160" height="22" as="geometry" /></mxCell>
    <mxCell id="4" value="Concept Activation Score Matrix
[N_samples × K_concepts]  (sparse, ≥0)
Each entry = fraction of patches → that concept
Same format for image and lab domains" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#fff2cc;strokeColor=#d6b656;fontSize=10;align=left;verticalAlign=top;" vertex="1" parent="1"><mxGeometry x="380" y="90" width="420" height="65" as="geometry" /></mxCell>
    <mxCell id="5" value="Logistic Regression  (Linear Probe)
fit(concept_scores, class_labels)

Class weights balanced (handles imbalance)
Regularisation: L2, C tuned via cross-validation
Coefficients: w_kc = contribution of concept k to class c" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#dae8fc;strokeColor=#6c8ebf;fontStyle=1;fontSize=9;align=center;" vertex="1" parent="1"><mxGeometry x="380" y="165" width="420" height="85" as="geometry" /></mxCell>
    <mxCell id="6" value="Class Prediction
argmax(softmax(W · concept_scores + b))

Image: Cat / Car / Bird
Lab:   Diabetes / Hypertension / Normal" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#d5e8d4;strokeColor=#82b366;fontStyle=1;fontSize=9;align=center;" vertex="1" parent="1"><mxGeometry x="380" y="260" width="420" height="65" as="geometry" /></mxCell>
    <mxCell id="7" value="Concept Contribution Explanation
For prediction of class c:
  contribution_k  =  w_kc × score_k
Ranked bar chart of concept contributions
Human-readable because concepts are named" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#ffe6cc;strokeColor=#d6b656;fontStyle=1;fontSize=9;align=center;" vertex="1" parent="1"><mxGeometry x="380" y="335" width="420" height="75" as="geometry" /></mxCell>
