    <mxCell id="11" value="Image Domain
Explanation Output" style="rounded=0;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#1565C0;fontColor=#ffffff;strokeColor=#1565C0;fontStyle=1;fontSize=12;align=center;" vertex="1" parent="1"><mxGeometry x="50" y="335" width="290" height="30" as="geometry" /></mxCell>
    <mxCell id="12" value="Panel 1 — Original Image
Full 224×224 with predicted class label
&quot;Predicted: Cat  (confidence 91%)&quot;" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#dae8fc;strokeColor=#6c8ebf;fontSize=10;align=left;verticalAlign=top;" vertex="1" parent="1"><mxGeometry x="50" y="373" width="290" height="55" as="geometry" /></mxCell>
    <mxCell id="13" value="Panel 2 — Concept Activation Map
Colour overlay showing which image
patches belong to which named concept
(e.g. red = cat_ear, blue = cat_fur)" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#dae8fc;strokeColor=#6c8ebf;fontSize=10;align=left;verticalAlign=top;" vertex="1" parent="1"><mxGeometry x="50" y="438" width="290" height="65" as="geometry" /></mxCell>
    <mxCell id="14" value="Panel 3 — Contribution Bar Chart
Horizontal bars per concept
Signed: positive = supports class,
negative = contra-indicates class" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#dae8fc;strokeColor=#6c8ebf;fontSize=10;align=left;verticalAlign=top;" vertex="1" parent="1"><mxGeometry x="50" y="513" width="290" height="65" as="geometry" /></mxCell>
    <mxCell id="15" value="Lab Domain
Explanation Output" style="rounded=0;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#2E7D32;fontColor=#ffffff;strokeColor=#2E7D32;fontStyle=1;fontSize=12;align=center;" vertex="1" parent="1"><mxGeometry x="840" y="335" width="310" height="30" as="geometry" /></mxCell>
    <mxCell id="16" value="Prediction + Confidence
&quot;Predicted: Diabetes  (probability 0.82)&quot;
Concept scores that drove the prediction
listed in descending order of contribution" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#d5e8d4;strokeColor=#82b366;fontSize=10;align=left;verticalAlign=top;" vertex="1" parent="1"><mxGeometry x="840" y="373" width="310" height="65" as="geometry" /></mxCell>
    <mxCell id="17" value="Clinical Concept Trace
Top contributing concepts:
  1. CBC: iron-deficiency anaemia pattern (+0.41)
  2. BMP: hyperglycaemia pattern (+0.38)
  3. Lipid: dyslipidaemia pattern (+0.21)
All concepts are human-validated labels" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#d5e8d4;strokeColor=#82b366;fontSize=10;align=left;verticalAlign=top;" vertex="1" parent="1"><mxGeometry x="840" y="448" width="310" height="90" as="geometry" /></mxCell>
    <mxCell id="18" value="Auditability Statement
&quot;Prediction driven by 3 clinical concepts
discovered without supervision.
Each concept was validated by a clinician.
No black-box features used.&quot;" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#d5e8d4;strokeColor=#82b366;fontSize=10;align=left;verticalAlign=top;" vertex="1" parent="1"><mxGeometry x="840" y="548" width="310" height="65" as="geometry" /></mxCell>
    <mxCell id="19" value="image" style="endArrow=open;endFill=0;dashed=1;strokeColor=#1565C0;strokeWidth=1.5;" edge="1" source="7" target="12" parent="1"><mxGeometry relative="1" as="geometry" /></mxCell>
    <mxCell id="20" value="lab" style="endArrow=open;endFill=0;dashed=1;strokeColor=#2E7D32;strokeWidth=1.5;" edge="1" source="7" target="16" parent="1"><mxGeometry relative="1" as="geometry" /></mxCell>
    <mxCell id="21" value="Ablation: Concept Classifier vs Black-box Baseline
Concept-based LogReg  vs  LogReg on raw features
Metric: AUC, accuracy, F1
Expected: comparable accuracy, full explainability
&quot;Interpretability trade-off is honest and quantified&quot;" style="text;html=1;strokeColor=none;fillColor=#fffde7;align=left;verticalAlign=top;whiteSpace=wrap;rounded=1;strokeColor=#f9a825;fontSize=9;fontStyle=2;" vertex="1" parent="1"><mxGeometry x="380" y="430" width="420" height="80" as="geometry" /></mxCell>
    <mxCell id="22" value="Key Dissertation Claim
&quot;Concepts discovered without supervision
predict clinical diagnoses they were never
trained on — and produce auditable
explanations traceable to named concepts.&quot;" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#ffe6cc;strokeColor=#d6b656;fontStyle=1;fontSize=9;align=center;" vertex="1" parent="1"><mxGeometry x="380" y="525" width="420" height="80" as="geometry" /></mxCell>
